\b\fs28 Installation
\b0\fs24 \
\
Download the latest version from the website or build from source using Xcode. Mount the dmg-file by opening it and copy the bundled 
\f1\fs26 .app
\f0\fs24  into your Applications-folder.\
\

\b\fs28 Usage
\b0\fs24 \
\
Drag & drop movie files and folders to Undertext.app and it'll launch to search for subtitles. You can also use "Open..." in the application menu after the application has started. Select the subtitles you want to download in the list of results and click "Download selected". Voil\'e0!\
